org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware.legacy

Class Hanger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware.Mechanism
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.hardware.legacy.Hanger

  • public class Hanger
extends Mechanism
    Hanger is the class that is used to define all of the hardware for a robot's hanger. Hanger must be instantiated, then initialized using init() before being used. This class also contains autonomous actions involving the hanger.
